    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>尝尝撒旦舞会的滋味！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>地狱万岁！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就像任何派对：宾客越疯狂，空间越狭小，舞会拖得越久——就越混乱。 <br>邀请、移动、提拔，再为葡萄酒献祭宾客：一边压住混沌，一边揭开黑暗圣经的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/5beb008a16be5ec9514e2fbd4ca98ea2.poster.avif?t=1770882496\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/5beb008a16be5ec9514e2fbd4ca98ea2.webm?t=1770882496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/5beb008a16be5ec9514e2fbd4ca98ea2.mp4?t=1770882496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>酒即是血，血即是酒。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你献祭宾客，把他们的血变成酒。酒很有用：用它让会场降温、压住混沌；或用来增强你自己的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/ab6b7074dff69e9663501e5b070fb89b.poster.avif?t=1770882496\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/ab6b7074dff69e9663501e5b070fb89b.webm?t=1770882496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/ab6b7074dff69e9663501e5b070fb89b.mp4?t=1770882496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>撒旦圣经藏着秘密。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成任务，书写黑暗圣经的篇章。每一卷揭示的，都是只能用鲜血写下的知识。翻开页面——亲眼看看其中写着什么。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/69a44d29081cab08c850809ecf06b522.poster.avif?t=1770882496\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/69a44d29081cab08c850809ecf06b522.webm?t=1770882496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/69a44d29081cab08c850809ecf06b522.mp4?t=1770882496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每一场舞会，都更盛大！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩大舞会容量，并在舞会进行时强化你对会场的控制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/c9e02e9b7cca7a03b6503bbec9559f1e.poster.avif?t=1770882496\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/c9e02e9b7cca7a03b6503bbec9559f1e.webm?t=1770882496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313990/extras/c9e02e9b7cca7a03b6503bbec9559f1e.mp4?t=1770882496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>社会模拟：</strong>宾客有偏好、黑粉与影响力。管理、操控、拖拽（Drag &amp; Drop）、提拔——然后惩罚。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理宾客：</strong>选择谁能入场，合并宾客让他们更有价值；拖拽（Drag &amp; Drop）宾客，让会场降温或升温。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心理恐怖：</strong>作为地狱之主，揭开人性的黑暗小径，让他们用血腥献祭为罪孽买单。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>元进程：</strong>完成任务，书写黑暗圣经的篇章，揭开它所藏的秘密知识。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特体验：</strong>就像活人的世界一样，撒旦的舞会永远让你措手不及。试着让舞会按你的意愿发展。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>舞会更新：</strong>用葡萄酒抬高宾客的地位、提升他们的价值；扩张你的领地，增强你对宾客的支配与权势。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏也许会改变你看待社会的方式——也许不会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但至少，你可以扮演撒旦，想象自己正在惩罚那些黑粉。</p>",
